high_descs: Go to the kitchen and then left to the counter next to the stove.

Go around the counter to the other side.

Go to the refrigerator on the right.
Place the chef's knife on the bottom shelf in the refrigerator.

Take two slices of bread.
Go back to the refrigerator.
Place the slices of bread in the freezer.

Pick up a slice of bread
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Place the bread next to the knife.
